    "description": "Surreal Nightmare 是一款潜行生存恐怖游戏，讲述的是实验室创造的野兽逃脱并在洞穴深处打开一个洞的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/faeb2da36d4413b77245092279bf404f.poster.avif?t=1722213839\" width=636 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/faeb2da36d4413b77245092279bf404f.webm?t=1722213839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/faeb2da36d4413b77245092279bf404f.mp4?t=1722213839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>雷切尔是一位在实验室工作的年轻女子，醒来时发现自己挂在绳子上，面对着野兽<br>她的目标是生存并进入设施，并找到出口，以便在事情脱离轨道之前快速逃脱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/6f7a537d06c60a4a68a6d409b8cc1503.poster.avif?t=1722213839\" width=636 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/6f7a537d06c60a4a68a6d409b8cc1503.webm?t=1722213839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867330/extras/6f7a537d06c60a4a68a6d409b8cc1503.mp4?t=1722213839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
